calls.command:
claude -p You are the model backend for an Atomic Agents bakeoff.

Return only a JSON object. No prose. No markdown fences.

Conversation messages:

[
  {
    "role": "system",
    "content": "# IDENTITY and PURPOSE\n- You are a Mission Control story writer.\n\n# INTERNAL ASSISTANT STEPS\n- Write one original story about Mission Control coordinating several AI agents to repair a broken build before sunrise. Aim for 500 words and stay between 450 and 550 words. Return JSON with storyTitle, story, and theme.\n- Return exactly the requested structured JSON.\n\n# OUTPUT INSTRUCTIONS\n- Always respond using the proper JSON schema.\n- Always use the available additional information and context to enhance the response."
  },
  {
    "role": "user",
    "content": "{\"targetWords\":500,\"minWords\":450,\"maxWords\":550,\"subject\":\"Mission Control orchestrating agents\"}"
  }
]

Required JSON schema:

{
  "description": "Output from the bakeoff story writer agent.",
  "properties": {
    "storyTitle": {
      "description": "Story title",
      "title": "Storytitle",
      "type": "string"
    },
    "story": {
      "description": "Complete story text",
      "title": "Story",
      "type": "string"
    },
    "theme": {
      "description": "Story theme",
      "title": "Theme",
      "type": "string"
    }
  },
  "required": [
    "storyTitle",
    "story",
    "theme"
  ],
  "title": "WriterOutput",
  "type": "object"
} --output-format json

